      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Event和Reminder是实体对象，EventDAO是数据访问层，ReminderService处理提醒调度。那基础设施这块怎么体现？比如WorkerNode、EtcdCluster这些？",
